罗比·威廉姆斯谈利亚姆·佩恩的挣扎：“他的考验和磨难与我的非常相似” https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-Trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=罗比·威廉姆斯谈利亚姆·佩恩的挣扎，他的考验和磨难与我的非常相似Laura MolloyFri, 18 Oct 2024 10:17:12 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3804014 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “31岁时，我的心魔仍然存在。我旧病复发。我很痛苦。我很痛苦，因为我旧病复发”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-the-struggles-of-liam-payne-his-trials-and-tribulations-were-very-similar-to-mine-3804014">罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams) 讲述利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 的挣扎：“他的考验和磨难与我的非常相似”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robbie-Williams-and-Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Unique-Nicole_Getty-Images-and-Jamie-McCarthy_Getty-Images-for-MTV-DIRECTV-NOW-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne)</a> 31 岁英年早逝后向他表示哀悼。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>周三晚（10月16日），有消息称佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡。据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/17/liam-payne-died-of-multiple-traumas-and-internal-and-external-bleeding" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，阿根廷检察官办公室透露，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p>威廉姆斯在他的 Instagram 账户上发表声明，与其他人一起向佩恩致敬，他写道，得知佩恩去世的消息后，他感到“震惊、悲伤和困惑”。</p><p>回忆起他在 2010 年为佩恩的前乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>参加<em>X Factor</em>比赛期间担任导师的经历。威廉姆斯写道：“我在倒括号中使用“指导”这个词，因为说实话，我几乎没有做任何事情。我只是和他们一起出去玩。他们都很厚脸皮又可爱。我喜欢那种轻松愉快的撒尿行为，并且一直想着当我在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">《Take That》</a>时，我就是那个厚脸皮的与流行歌星一起撒尿的人。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803862" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803862" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803862" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-1D-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803862" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Stephane Cardinale – Corbis/Corbis via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “从那天起我们的道路就交叉了，我都很喜欢他们。利亚姆所经历的考验和磨难与我的非常相似，因此伸出援手并提供我所能提供的帮助是有意义的。所以我就这么做了。”</p><p>这位前 Take That 主唱 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-opens-up-about-past-self-harming-3528952">此前曾公开讲述过他的自残和抑郁史</a>，并鼓励人们对自己在公众眼中发表的评论更加“谨慎”。</p><p>威廉姆斯接着说道：“我已经 31 岁了，心里的恶魔仍然存在。我旧病复发。我很痛苦。我很痛苦，因为我复发了。由于多种痛苦的原因，我旧病复发。我记得希斯·莱杰经过时心想“我就是下一个”。感谢上帝的恩典和/或运气不好我还在这里。</p><p> “不幸的是，互联网将继续是互联网。不幸的是，媒体将继续成为媒体，名声将继续成为名声。</p><p> “作为个人，我们有能力改变自己。我们可以更友善一些。我们可以更加富有同理心。我们至少可以尝试对自己、家人、朋友、生活中的陌生人和互联网上的陌生人更加富有同情心。”</p><p>他继续说道：“真是一个英俊有才华的男孩。对于他的朋友、家人、粉丝来说，以及这一刻所创造的能量——整个世界来说，这是多么悲惨的痛苦损失。”</p><p>请阅读下面他的完整声明。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBQkh7zOAjr/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C5