3524" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803524" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803524" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803524" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Karwai Tang/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>奥斯本向佩恩致敬之前，与 One Direction 一起参加选秀节目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·威塞尔 (Katie Waissel)</a>发表评论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“对年轻艺术家的关心和支持</a>”。同样，在同一季节目中获得第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">在向佩恩致敬的同时，也公开反对“对年轻明星的剥削和牟取暴利”。</a></p><p>于 2018 年结束的<em>《X Factor</em> 》还在社交媒体上分享了一条信息，写道：“利亚姆非常有才华，作为 One Direction 的一员，利亚姆将为音乐行业和世界各地的歌迷留下持久的遗产。”</p><p>昨天（10 月 17 日），One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈利·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">就佩恩的去世发表了一份联合声明，他们在声明中表达了他们的悲痛，并表示他们需要时间“哀悼并处理我们失去的人”。哥哥，我们深爱的人。”</a></p><p>斯泰尔斯、汤姆林森和马利克也分享了他们自己的个人声明， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-remembers-liam-payne-in-tribute-post-it-was-an-honour-to-be-alongside-him-3803922">斯泰尔斯写道</a>：我对利亚姆的去世感到非常震惊。他最大的快乐就是让别人快乐，能和他一起做这件事是他的荣幸。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBPiO3bofS4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.4