/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_elton_john_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_elton_john_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_elton_john_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕（Dua Lipa）</a>昨晚（10月17日，星期四）在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅（Royal Albert Hall）进行了一次特别的一次演出，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ELTON-JOHN">埃尔顿·约翰爵士（Elton John</a> Sir Cold Heart）在舞台上加入了她的演出。在下面查看镜头，照片等。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/dua-lipa-cover-interview-2020-if-somebody-told-me-not-to-discuss-issues-im-passionate-about-i-wouldnt-listen-2644409"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>杜阿·莱帕（Dua Lipa）在封面上：“如果有人告诉我不要讨论我热衷的问题吗？我不会听”</a></li></ul><p>该节目以43件式的遗产乐团以及14个合唱团和7件乐队的乐队为特色，看到Lipa在标志性场地中心的回合中表演，以表演以后拍摄的节目。</p><p>这位歌手在给予“时代的终结”并给予“ Houdini”詹姆斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">·</a><em>邦德（James Bond</em> ）主题待遇的“时代”之后对人群讲话时，这位歌手告诉观众（他带着“打扮成印象深刻的备忘录”）如何将表演融合在一起是“梦想”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803988" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803988" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803988" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1.jpg" alt="Dua Lipa在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅直播。学分：劳埃德·韦克菲尔德（Lloyd Wakefield）" width="1600" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1.jpg 1600w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_1-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803988" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅直播。学分：劳埃德·韦克菲尔德（Lloyd Wakefield）</figcaption></figure><p>她说：“我一直很期待这个节目，这是我比其他任何人都更期待的节目。”与遗产乐团一起在一个看到温斯顿·丘吉尔（Winston Churchill），查尔斯·戴高勒（Charles de Gaulle）和艾伯特·爱因斯坦（Albert Einstein）之类的场所 - 开玩笑说，这三人都没有和她的舞者一起表演，而且她“几乎可以肯定他们没有一件衣服那样好。</p><p>在为“玛丽亚”的现场亮相和“法国出口”的现场演出发作后，杜阿<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cleo-sol">·</a>利帕（Dua Lipa让我搬我”，今晚与如此宏伟的狂热一起在这里播放它很“合适”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803989" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803989" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803989" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2.jpg" alt="Dua Lipa在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅直播。学分：劳埃德·韦克菲尔德（Lloyd Wakefield）" width="1600" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2.jpg 1600w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dua_lipa_Lloyd-Wakefield_2-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803989" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa在伦敦的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅直播。学分：劳埃德·韦克菲尔德（Lloyd Wakefield）</figcaption></figure><p>最终，利帕（Lipa）说，在用乐团重新构想她的音乐时，“到达音乐的裸露骨头真是太有趣了，这是她最近专辑“激进乐观”的“有机声音”，到目前为止，这一时刻都为我们买了。</p><p>杜阿·丽帕（Dua Lipa）返回再来一次，陷入了“冷心”，然后透露埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）隐藏在一系列支持歌手后面，加入了她的巨大欢迎合作 - 引起了观众的狂热掌声。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/elton-john-cover-interview-2021-the-lockdown-sessions-3075718">埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）在封面上：“我对过去不感兴趣 - 甚至没有埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）的过去”</a></strong></li></ul><p>场景以热门歌曲的“ Be One”，“舞会舞会”（她的<em>芭比娃娃</em>配乐中的歌曲）的现场处女作和“不要现在开始”的巨大结局 - 杜阿·莉帕（Dua Lipa）邀请她的舞者，返回以进行壮观的关闭。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBQdIaPgDqP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.11